{"tid":1779573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［反醒］有個隻腳中過實彈嘅勇武 喊住講咗一段說話（有片）佢都未放棄 希望大家都可以堅持","createTime":"2019-12-11T18:25:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T15:53:46.000Z","uid":65210,"like":71,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"ef31fedfb6a151370ccf5509b6882fabf0ffc969","tid":1779573,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T18:25:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/hkmagicresearchschool\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkmagicresearchschool&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnADk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=2e9c845f\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkmagicresearchschool</a><br />\n我係呢個Channel到睇到嘅 香港魔法研究學院<br />\n請睇片聽清楚手足講嘅野<br />\n（最新段片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aFJ8bes.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaFJ8bes.jpg&h=f0c0e7ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RKJDysO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRKJDysO.jpg&h=4695211f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iGG9E7P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiGG9E7P.jpg&h=c7f2ea9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e7X5dsQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe7X5dsQ.jpg&h=cc2edd05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n文字版 &mdash; <br />\n白衫手足：（喊住講）<br />\n我隻腳咁樣 到底點打啊？<br />\n<br />\nBlack block手足：<br />\n我隻腳都傷咗㗎 我隻腳都中咗子彈㗎<br />\n係子彈啊 唔係橡膠（子彈）我都中咗㗎<br />\n（越來越激動 開始喊）<br />\n我都企咗係到啊 你地都一定得㗎<br />\n好辛苦啊 我都好辛苦啊<br />\n我自己有一條路可以Quit game 走㗎<br />\n點解我仲要留係到Full gear啊<br />\n<br />\n我真係好想好想你地都可以 我係留係到㗎咋<br />\n我地唔可以輸比政府㗎<br />\n我真係好想贏啊 我想贏一次<br />\n我唔想再輸一個人啦<br />\n佢返到去係會打你㗎<br />\n我都係和平比人拉 我唔係做好多野比人拉<br />\n我就係做和理非都比人拉<br />\n我一入到去我比人拉啊 係唔係啊<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">落場有咩拗撬唔好互屌  好似black block手足咁 <br />\n佢唔係開口：「我屌你老母我隻腳中撚咗實彈都企咗係到啦 你走去邊撚到啊！」</span></strong><br />\n唔好開親口就屌鳩手足 客氣小小<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 唔完美嘅就要改善<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bipWj7R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbipWj7R.png&h=22afa3be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好放棄 千祈唔好放棄<br />\n呢半年證明咗只有堅持先會有希望<br />\n憑住香港係世界春袋  周圍幫中共辣火頭 </span></strong><br />\n有幾多人2014年就已經對香港心鳩灰<br />\n一另轉面 無撚曬人<br />\n龍和道爆曬頭 夏愨道歌舞昇平<br />\n邊個估到2019年 我地示威示到法國人都要connect我地<br />\n智利要開研討會抄考<br />\n我地又成功辣到環保議題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拍拖拍咗半年都會有平台期 運動有冷卻都好正常<br />\n唔係話日日都要落場先叫抗爭緊<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">但係<br />\n記住所有已離世義士 及前線手足嘅付出犧牲<br />\n請對運動保持認真態度 <br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n尤其係某一啲嘅藝術和理非 唔好再玩膠 <br />\n你覺得好藝術 好大愛 畫面好靚 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pkW5X0L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpkW5X0L.png&h=c068ef6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">流血個個唔係咁諗 <br />\n死咗個仔 死咗朋友嘅人唔係咁諗<br />\n麻煩諗真啲咩叫尊重<br />\n唔好掛住搞藝術 搞眾籌<br />\n前線已經五癆七傷 為咗落場<br />\n工又無得返 只可以返散工 <br />\n錢又無 好多同屋企人 另一半嘈大交分開曬<br />\n吸TG吸到又咳又痾 肺都爛埋<br />\n撞到瘀曬 跌斷腳都當係小事 <br />\n中海綿彈橡膠彈已經係日常</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n懇求大家認真地易位而處<br />\n認下做前線個班到底付出咗幾多野<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">屠龍一隊有曬證據非法藏有鎗械 有機會要坐一世<br />\n諗下佢地嘅決心<br />\n再諗下 自己係咪可以做得更多<br />\n唔好再只repost笑狗嘅Meme就當自己係深黃 做咗野</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n諗返起6月7 月 <br />\n7.21個排嘅抗爭習慣你仲有無繼續？<br />\n搭車放工仲有無air drop文宣？<br />\n買日用品係咪可以幫襯光時 ？<br />\n日常買野有無揀咗幫襯小商戶先？<br />\n百佳 同 惠康（怡和）係咪已經慣咗幫襯誠哥先？<br />\n每次出街食飯 有無開黃藍地圖？<br />\n和理非嘅遊行集會 有無盡量出席<br />\n出糧有無習慣捐小小比小朋友 立場 星火 傳真社<br />\n仲有無幫手貼文宣<br />\n老豆搵出黎啲仔 有無幫手寫係街到實體化<br />\n有好多日常嘅抗爭習慣 <br />\n唔好因為事小而不為<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Sor for 1999<br />\n總之堅持 尊重 唔放棄<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c3c27fbc9bc3fb359c09a48b2a267fb25f0d95b0","tid":1779573,"uid":47565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T18:26:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"21fe9eed0ce253684e18a856c0312df409b3db9b","tid":1779573,"uid":65210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T18:26:56.000Z","msg":"唔好習慣 唔好咁快遺忘<br />\n求求各位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"139a0fa4d494855018601b11cc214362fca550d2","tid":1779573,"uid":65210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T18:29:50.000Z","msg":"17:00-20:00 <br />\n大圍寶福山<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2zp7r52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2zp7r52.jpg&h=eb447530&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc7d2bfc188855de44cd3ddef466f5d2421504a4","tid":1779573,"uid":65210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T18:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5KSAAZL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5KSAAZL.jpg&h=949a8e0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每一槍，都不能忘記。<br />\n2019年，由初夏到寒冬，瘋警殺紅了眼，謀殺香港人。<br />\n自6月9日至今，警方已拘捕6022人，年齡介乎11至84歲，當中有2393人是學生，接近總被捕人士達四成。<br />\n共使用16000枚催淚彈、10000發橡膠子彈、2000發布袋彈、約1850發海綿彈。<br />\n#五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nextmagazinefansclub/photos/a.124899627673989/1430693370427935/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnextmagazinefansclub%2Fphotos%2Fa.124899627673989%2F1430693370427935%2F&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnADk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=2e73e5f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nextmagazinefansclub/photos/a.124899627673989/1430693370427935/</a>"},{"pid":"f1e56ef6c19064770297d937df72ac20